value.0: This stern young woman bears a haughty demeanor and her stylish clothing seems to be at odds with the relative humility of her home. She has the look of someone who has only recently come into money.
This practical garb was worn by Ilsa Steinfaar, a mine-owner's wife in the northern Barrow Dwarf community of Brogan's Arm.
Fashioned from rough-hewn wood, this simple door swings on ill-fitting hinges.
